OL,3,CMotorcyclist killed in collision with
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,FA motorcyclist has been killed after
OL,7,Fhis bike collided with a car in
OL,8,FFarnborough.
OL,10,FPolice are investigating the fatal
OL,11,Fcollision which occurred on Friday 22
OL,12,FMay.
OL,14,FOfficers were called to the crash just
OL,15,Fbfore 7:30am on Prospect Road which
OL,16,Finvolved a silver Vauxhall Corsa and a
OL,17,Fsilver Suzuki motorbike.
OL,19,FThe rider of the motorbike, a 43-year-
OL,20,Fold man, was pronounced dead at the
OL,21,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
